WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.990
=Episode 16=

01:45.550 --> 01:47.340
Yan Zhang, Vice Lord of Xuling Temple,

01:48.190 --> 01:49.700
did a great job planning for me.

01:50.300 --> 01:51.470
Give him 10,000 spirit stones.

01:54.420 --> 01:56.220
Farewell, Your Grace.

02:05.580 --> 02:07.220
I haven't seen this sword in ages.

02:08.070 --> 02:09.900
You're the new owner of the Deliverance?

02:10.140 --> 02:11.020
You know

02:11.020 --> 02:11.860
the former owner?

02:12.300 --> 02:13.550
Former owner?

02:14.140 --> 02:16.140
Isn't it just Hejia Jixi,

02:16.390 --> 02:17.390
the forger of this sword

02:17.390 --> 02:18.510
and Simu's aunt?

02:20.670 --> 02:21.510
What?

02:21.740 --> 02:22.790
Simu didn't tell you

02:22.790 --> 02:24.070
the story behind this sword?

02:24.860 --> 02:26.620
Looks like the two of you

02:26.620 --> 02:28.140
aren't very close.

02:32.070 --> 02:32.910
My Lady,

02:33.740 --> 02:35.620
do you know about Simu's parents,

02:35.620 --> 02:36.580
her uncle and aunt?

02:39.020 --> 02:40.670
I got on very well

02:40.900 --> 02:42.510
with them.

02:43.950 --> 02:45.990
When the previous sovereign was here,

02:45.990 --> 02:48.580
he called me Lady Jiang Ai.

02:49.110 --> 02:50.950
Simu calls me

02:50.950 --> 02:52.180
the way her father did.

02:53.580 --> 02:54.620
Then can you tell me

02:54.830 --> 02:56.180
about her childhood?

02:59.550 --> 03:00.390
Young man,

03:01.140 --> 03:02.830
it's not fun to inquire

03:03.230 --> 03:04.990
about the Sovereign's past.

03:05.990 --> 03:07.070
It's not for fun.

03:08.070 --> 03:09.110
I want to know about her.

03:14.180 --> 03:15.230
In that case,

03:15.550 --> 03:16.860
how many spirit stones can you offer?

03:17.700 --> 03:18.540
Spirit stones?

03:19.550 --> 03:20.740
Money of the Void?

03:24.670 --> 03:26.270
Information about the Sovereign

03:26.270 --> 03:28.110
will certainly fetch a good price.

03:28.740 --> 03:30.070
How come I didn't think

03:30.070 --> 03:31.180
of this great business?

03:35.020 --> 03:35.860
Young man,

03:36.550 --> 03:37.510
a discount for you.

03:39.070 --> 03:40.180
Half a million.

03:41.460 --> 03:43.230
When you have enough money,

03:43.460 --> 03:44.830
come to me for her information.

03:45.740 --> 03:46.620
Half a million?

03:48.110 --> 03:49.420
That doesn't sound cheap at all.

03:51.550 --> 03:52.670
You aren't the only one

03:52.670 --> 03:54.110
who adores Simu.

03:54.830 --> 03:56.230
You'd better be careful.

04:10.950 --> 04:11.790
Your Lordship,

04:13.110 --> 04:14.110
we meet again.

04:15.740 --> 04:16.910
You must be

04:16.910 --> 04:18.180
that mortal general.

04:19.180 --> 04:20.820
I heard you brought Her Grace

04:20.990 --> 04:22.350
a lot of fun during her vacation.

04:23.110 --> 04:24.670
Your short stay in the Void

04:25.110 --> 04:26.910
is just a sign of her favor.

04:27.820 --> 04:29.180
It seems your sovereign

04:29.470 --> 04:30.790
speaks highly of me.

04:32.820 --> 04:33.860
I just wanted to see

04:33.860 --> 04:35.470
what Simu's place would look like.

04:35.910 --> 04:37.350
She approved right away.

04:37.350 --> 04:38.300
How dare you

04:38.620 --> 04:40.230
call Her Grace by name?

04:42.500 --> 04:44.300
How Simu and I call each other

04:45.180 --> 04:46.110
is our own business.

04:47.380 --> 04:48.740
You're in no position

04:48.950 --> 04:49.790
to get angry.

04:49.790 --> 04:50.790
How dare you!

05:04.110 --> 05:05.740
The curfew begins.

05:07.230 --> 05:08.590
Enjoy your stay.

05:14.100 --> 05:20.140
(Sovereign's Hall)

06:28.550 --> 06:29.990
I can't believe Simu has lived here

06:31.420 --> 06:32.550
for centuries now.

07:46.710 --> 07:48.230
Only your sovereign can eat me.

08:17.420 --> 08:20.620
(Lake Cottage, the Void)

08:28.500 --> 08:30.110
Didn't expect to find a place like this.

09:51.350 --> 09:53.860
Duan Shunxi, how bold of you.

09:54.950 --> 09:56.660
You fear no place, do you?

10:05.710 --> 10:06.900
I didn't know you were here.

10:07.470 --> 10:08.310
No offense.

10:09.070 --> 10:09.950
Please forgive me.

10:11.380 --> 10:12.660
This place is warded.

10:13.540 --> 10:14.710
How did you get in?

10:16.620 --> 10:18.230
Maybe this cottage likes me

10:18.950 --> 10:19.950
and allowed me in.

10:29.380 --> 10:30.230
Your Grace,

10:31.780 --> 10:32.830
nights here are cold.

10:34.310 --> 10:35.590
You'd really let me stay out?

11:25.780 --> 11:27.070
How did you find me?

11:32.590 --> 11:33.430
There's less

11:33.430 --> 11:34.380
discordant aura here.

11:35.380 --> 11:36.310
The scent of your sachet

11:36.860 --> 11:37.860
is actually stronger.

11:40.740 --> 11:42.350
What have you reflected on so far?

11:50.380 --> 11:51.220
I was thinking.

11:52.540 --> 11:53.380
When I kissed you,

11:54.830 --> 11:55.670
you remained silent

11:55.680 --> 11:56.520
and stared at me.

11:57.860 --> 11:58.860
What were you thinking?

12:00.070 --> 12:01.020
I was thinking,

12:02.110 --> 12:03.310
"When I get my power back,

12:04.140 --> 12:05.500
I'll make you regret it."

12:08.260 --> 12:09.110
Furthermore,

12:09.950 --> 12:11.260
I guess you were also thinking

12:12.350 --> 12:13.590
why I kissed you.

12:21.620 --> 12:22.460
You probably thought

12:22.460 --> 12:23.350
I was lost in passion

12:23.990 --> 12:25.140
and it was a passing fancy.

12:27.380 --> 12:28.470
But soon you realized

12:29.110 --> 12:30.070
that you were wrong.

12:34.710 --> 12:36.110
You realized that I was serious.

12:37.020 --> 12:38.260
So you didn't say anything.

12:39.430 --> 12:40.310
Even today,

12:41.140 --> 12:42.590
you only hung me on the palace gate

12:44.430 --> 12:45.350
to scare me off,

12:46.430 --> 12:47.270
rather than kill me.

12:48.470 --> 12:49.310
Right?

12:56.620 --> 12:58.140
That day, I was really lost in passion.

13:00.620 --> 13:01.830
I thought you were so adorable

13:02.500 --> 13:03.980
and I would never meet another girl

13:03.980 --> 13:04.990
like you.

13:07.380 --> 13:08.430
And I'd never feel the same

13:12.230 --> 13:13.140
for anyone else.

13:21.020 --> 13:22.110
I've calmed down these days

13:23.110 --> 13:24.020
and thought about it.

13:27.230 --> 13:28.310
That's absolutely true.

13:40.710 --> 13:42.860
Young people usually
have fleeting affections.

13:43.860 --> 13:45.430
It's not strange that you like me.

13:46.660 --> 13:47.500
I've seen

13:47.500 --> 13:48.540
a lot of men like you.

13:49.660 --> 13:50.590
Among them,

13:50.590 --> 13:51.540
you're the smartest one.

13:53.070 --> 13:54.110
In that case,

13:55.710 --> 13:57.430
you should think before you speak.

13:59.280 --> 14:00.140
I've thought it over.

14:00.140 --> 14:00.980
No, you haven't.

14:01.950 --> 14:02.830
Do you really know me?

14:04.950 --> 14:05.860
I want to know you.

14:07.110 --> 14:08.190
And I'm getting to know you,

14:11.620 --> 14:12.460
bit by bit.

14:13.990 --> 14:15.070
This room, for example.

14:16.830 --> 14:17.780
I guess it was the room

14:17.780 --> 14:18.620
you once lived in

14:18.950 --> 14:20.190
with your parents.

14:21.140 --> 14:22.430
And the toys on the shelves.

14:23.700 --> 14:24.540
They were your toys.

14:24.540 --> 14:25.580
You shouldn't have come.

14:37.460 --> 14:39.420
(Sovereign's Hall)

14:51.180 --> 14:53.740
(Sovereign's Hall)

15:39.340 --> 15:43.050
♪Falling down like snow♪

15:43.520 --> 15:47.000
♪Joys and sorrows of the mortal world♪

15:47.000 --> 15:50.880
♪Swept along by the daylight♪

15:51.290 --> 15:55.090
♪The forms and hues of the mortal realm♪

15:55.360 --> 15:58.030
♪Lingering for a fleeting moment♪

15:58.190 --> 16:02.510
♪Was once touched by laughing tears♪

16:02.990 --> 16:05.900
♪If I could live a simple life♪

16:05.900 --> 16:06.740
♪For once♪

16:06.740 --> 16:11.820
♪I'd be a guest in a sweet dream♪

16:13.910 --> 16:17.410
♪Dawn and dusk rise and set♪

16:17.680 --> 16:21.210
♪Longing to meet, yet parted by destiny♪

16:21.720 --> 16:25.330
♪Let me wander through♪

16:25.330 --> 16:28.320
♪Light and dark, without turning back♪

16:28.350 --> 16:29.190
You know what?

16:29.190 --> 16:30.190
Her Grace and Lord Yan Ke

16:30.430 --> 16:31.780
are fixing Fusang Tree so early.

16:32.260 --> 16:33.350
Their intimacy

16:33.660 --> 16:34.540
makes us jealous.

16:35.260 --> 16:36.790
Everybody knows their relationship.

16:36.990 --> 16:38.620
Her Grace just hasn't acknowledged him.

16:39.930 --> 16:45.840
♪Whether I stay or go, I'm all alone♪

16:48.110 --> 16:49.310
With your spirit power,

16:49.620 --> 16:51.020
the tree is growing stronger.

16:51.660 --> 16:52.860
Simu, you must be tired.

16:53.470 --> 16:54.350
Get some rest.

16:55.860 --> 16:56.710
All right, Yan.

17:00.040 --> 17:03.770
♪As stars shift and change places♪

17:03.860 --> 17:07.520
♪A century is like a dream♪

17:07.800 --> 17:11.270
♪Let me journey across them all♪

17:11.380 --> 17:15.200
♪Without reincarnations♪

17:15.580 --> 17:19.050
♪A lone lamp shines on the other shore♪

17:19.140 --> 17:22.910
♪Accompanied by the abyss♪

17:23.210 --> 17:26.120
♪Moments may last♪

17:27.780 --> 17:28.620
Your Lordship.

17:29.540 --> 17:30.670
Are you really surprised

17:30.820 --> 17:31.990
to see me alive?

17:36.190 --> 17:38.150
The spirit that attacked me yesterday

17:39.150 --> 17:40.710
had the same aura as yours.

17:43.580 --> 17:44.820
You just can't smell it.

17:47.340 --> 17:49.100
I don't know what you're talking about.

17:49.580 --> 17:50.740
Perhaps we should

17:50.740 --> 17:51.580
talk frankly.

17:51.910 --> 17:52.780
Your Lordship,

17:52.780 --> 17:54.390
however much you hate me,

17:54.670 --> 17:55.870
you shouldn't kill me.

17:56.390 --> 17:57.670
If I died in the Void,

17:58.060 --> 17:59.910
what would become of Simu's honor

18:00.300 --> 18:01.140
and reputation?

18:04.500 --> 18:06.470
You're merely a lowly mortal

18:07.060 --> 18:08.740
and you may die in an instant.

18:08.950 --> 18:10.190
What right do you have

18:10.190 --> 18:11.740
to talk frankly with me?

18:12.740 --> 18:14.670
I'm not a lowly mortal, actually.

18:15.300 --> 18:16.500
I'm the only man the Sovereign

18:16.500 --> 18:17.340
has brought back

18:17.350 --> 18:18.500
in the past 300 years.

18:19.990 --> 18:20.830
In the Spirit World,

18:21.870 --> 18:23.300
only she can kill me.

18:27.870 --> 18:29.740
Then you'd better

18:29.740 --> 18:30.580
keep yourself alive.

18:57.990 --> 18:58.830
Hey, young man.

19:01.920 --> 19:02.780
Oh, it's you.

19:02.780 --> 19:03.870
What do you mean by that?

19:04.190 --> 19:05.060
You should say,

19:05.060 --> 19:06.020
"We meet again."

19:07.500 --> 19:08.340
I was sent here

19:08.340 --> 19:09.190
as your servant.

19:15.300 --> 19:16.190
What happened to you?

19:20.580 --> 19:21.420
Don't mention it.

19:21.650 --> 19:22.500
Song Xingyu

19:22.500 --> 19:23.710
completely ruined me.

19:24.540 --> 19:25.630
Having lost

19:25.630 --> 19:26.470
all my possessions,

19:26.670 --> 19:27.540
I'm now a servant.

19:28.100 --> 19:29.150
So I end up like this.

19:30.260 --> 19:31.470
You brought this upon yourself.

19:31.820 --> 19:32.660
No one is to blame.

19:33.060 --> 19:33.900
Young man,

19:34.230 --> 19:35.710
you're in no position to talk.

19:36.230 --> 19:37.190
I heard

19:37.430 --> 19:38.950
you offended Her Grace

19:39.100 --> 19:40.100
and were hung up there

19:40.100 --> 19:40.940
for humiliation.

19:41.540 --> 19:43.020
I would just be hung for a few days.

19:43.710 --> 19:44.820
Your 600-year-old treasures

19:44.820 --> 19:45.660
are all gone.

19:53.480 --> 19:54.340
What?

19:54.340 --> 19:55.180
Have you heard

19:55.710 --> 19:56.870
of the backside
of the Void Mountain?

19:58.630 --> 19:59.630
Why do you ask?

20:01.430 --> 20:02.710
That's a forbidden area here.

20:02.950 --> 20:03.950
Don't ask around.

20:04.250 --> 20:05.090
Forbidden area?

20:05.100 --> 20:05.950
Yeah.

20:05.960 --> 20:07.150
Only Her Grace is allowed in.

20:07.820 --> 20:08.910
Don't bring it up again.

20:10.580 --> 20:11.500
Does Her Grace

20:11.500 --> 20:12.470
usually live there?

20:13.470 --> 20:14.410
Her Grace certainly has

20:14.410 --> 20:15.440
her own sleeping hall.

20:15.630 --> 20:16.740
Without her permission,

20:16.740 --> 20:17.630
no one can get in.

20:24.630 --> 20:25.500
The curfew will begin.

20:25.500 --> 20:26.470
I'll come tomorrow.

20:53.020 --> 20:55.620
(Zhaomu Pavilion, the Void)

21:07.020 --> 21:08.500
This place isn't your house

21:08.820 --> 21:09.910
where you can go anywhere.

21:11.300 --> 21:12.140
Your Grace,

21:12.820 --> 21:13.660
I'm so sleepy.

21:14.710 --> 21:15.950
Let me get in for a nap.

21:21.910 --> 21:22.750
It's spacious out.

21:23.150 --> 21:23.990
Quite enough for you.

21:25.150 --> 21:26.630
You'd really let me sleep out here?

22:31.870 --> 22:33.300
You really make yourself comfortable.

22:46.470 --> 22:47.310
Get up.

22:54.060 --> 22:54.900
Stop pretending.

22:55.910 --> 22:56.820
Get out of my...

23:05.470 --> 23:06.310
Jiang Ai.

23:08.740 --> 23:09.580
Your Grace.

23:09.580 --> 23:10.420
Lady Jiang Ai.

23:13.060 --> 23:14.430
What's wrong with him?

23:21.670 --> 23:22.740
He's hungry.

23:26.300 --> 23:27.950
A mortal can't live without food.

23:29.990 --> 23:32.500
Time runs the same here.

23:32.950 --> 23:34.430
He hasn't eaten anything for two days.

23:34.430 --> 23:35.580
So he fainted from hunger.

23:40.430 --> 23:41.580
Prepare a meal for him.

23:42.260 --> 23:43.430
You're not really going

23:43.430 --> 23:44.780
to keep him here, are you?

23:45.870 --> 23:47.230
I don't want to keep him here.

23:47.500 --> 23:48.990
But I can't let him die of hunger.

23:49.630 --> 23:51.100
It's not easy to raise a mortal

23:51.100 --> 23:52.100
in our world.

23:54.580 --> 23:55.780
Feeding a mortal

23:55.780 --> 23:57.470
will cost a great many spirit stones.

24:02.670 --> 24:03.820
Whatever amount you need,

24:03.820 --> 24:05.020
I'll approve it.

24:09.630 --> 24:10.470
Simu,

24:10.670 --> 24:11.990
why don't you just

24:11.990 --> 24:12.990
acknowledge him?

24:13.710 --> 24:14.990
He's handsome,

24:14.990 --> 24:16.340
bold and cheerful.

24:16.540 --> 24:18.020
He cares a lot for you.

24:18.340 --> 24:19.190
If you ask me,

24:19.190 --> 24:21.670
he loves you more than anything.

24:24.710 --> 24:26.100
I can't let him stay forever.

24:28.740 --> 24:29.670
When he recovers,

24:30.780 --> 24:31.990
I'll send him back.

24:37.230 --> 24:38.300
I get it.

25:12.500 --> 25:13.820
Since you're awake, come and eat.

25:52.540 --> 25:53.580
I never expected

25:55.430 --> 25:56.670
to see mortal food here.

25:56.990 --> 25:58.190
It's a vast world.

25:58.500 --> 25:59.630
A table of mortal food

25:59.630 --> 26:00.540
isn't exactly rare.

26:13.260 --> 26:14.100
You don't dare?

26:18.870 --> 26:19.710
I can't bear to.

26:32.780 --> 26:33.670
After you're full,

26:34.100 --> 26:34.990
stay here for a rest.

26:36.190 --> 26:37.100
Thank you, Your Grace.

26:43.190 --> 26:44.300
It's where the spirits live.

26:45.260 --> 26:46.340
A mortal shouldn't linger.

26:48.710 --> 26:49.550
Foxy.

26:51.390 --> 26:52.390
You shouldn't have come.

27:26.990 --> 27:27.830
Yan.

27:30.870 --> 27:31.870
Got something to say?

27:36.190 --> 27:37.030
Simu,

27:37.480 --> 27:38.320
when will you

27:38.320 --> 27:39.500
send that mortal away?

27:45.430 --> 27:46.580
What do you think?

27:51.430 --> 27:52.990
The sooner, the better.

27:54.230 --> 27:56.100
Our world is no place for mortals.

27:56.500 --> 27:58.390
And Fusang Tree hasn't recovered.

27:58.950 --> 28:00.150
Spirits are piling up here.

28:00.670 --> 28:01.990
Who knows what will happen?

28:02.740 --> 28:03.820
We have no time

28:03.820 --> 28:05.060
to spare for a mortal's fate.

28:07.340 --> 28:08.180
Your Grace,

28:08.870 --> 28:10.060
this mortal

28:10.470 --> 28:11.630
has caused quite a commotion

28:11.630 --> 28:12.990
inside our world.

28:13.500 --> 28:14.500
If this goes on,

28:14.950 --> 28:16.820
it's hard to tell if there will be

28:17.230 --> 28:18.780
even more chaos.

28:22.300 --> 28:23.740
How could you think

28:24.390 --> 28:25.390
a mere mortal

28:25.390 --> 28:26.670
would destabilize the Void?

28:28.340 --> 28:29.870
If he really can,

28:30.390 --> 28:31.390
I'd like to see.

28:33.390 --> 28:34.230
Your Grace,

28:34.470 --> 28:35.540
that's not what I mean.

28:35.670 --> 28:36.510
Enough.

28:37.230 --> 28:38.190
I have my own plans

28:38.990 --> 28:40.100
about him.

28:57.740 --> 28:59.020
Why did you get up there again?

29:08.780 --> 29:09.620
Your Grace,

29:11.430 --> 29:12.820
you said three days.

29:13.990 --> 29:14.910
It's the last quarter.

29:15.060 --> 29:16.470
You're hopeless.

29:17.230 --> 29:18.540
You won't change anyway.

29:19.150 --> 29:20.260
Get out of my sight.

29:51.260 --> 29:52.470
This is a bitterly cold place.

29:52.780 --> 29:53.990
No mortal can endure that.

29:54.670 --> 29:55.870
He must not stay.

29:59.540 --> 30:00.780
This is not your concern.

30:46.900 --> 30:47.740
The chill here

30:47.740 --> 30:48.950
has even invaded your veins.

30:49.740 --> 30:50.580
You could've told me.

30:51.340 --> 30:52.300
If I had told you,

30:54.910 --> 30:55.760
wouldn't you have

30:55.760 --> 30:56.820
sent me away at once?

30:59.390 --> 31:00.230
Silly man.

31:15.740 --> 31:16.580
What's so funny?

31:18.300 --> 31:20.020
It seems ever since we met,

31:22.820 --> 31:24.580
you've been healing me.

31:26.020 --> 31:27.630
Or do you want to heal me?

31:40.910 --> 31:41.750
No.

31:44.230 --> 31:45.820
I never want you to get hurt.

32:16.870 --> 32:17.870
When the moon is full,

32:19.630 --> 32:21.100
the spirits' desires will grow strong.

32:22.500 --> 32:23.910
These are their painful moans

32:23.910 --> 32:25.470
for unattainable desires.

32:30.060 --> 32:30.900
Scared?

32:32.260 --> 32:33.100
Not really.

32:34.820 --> 32:36.100
It's just a little bit noisy.

32:40.020 --> 32:41.100
In the Void,

32:42.820 --> 32:43.710
living without senses

32:45.430 --> 32:46.580
might be a good thing.

32:47.260 --> 32:48.340
The mortal's senses

32:48.500 --> 32:50.230
will be infinitely amplified here.

32:53.100 --> 32:54.870
You really shouldn't stay.

33:00.020 --> 33:00.950
Life is short.

33:04.100 --> 33:05.020
I want to live my way.

33:13.230 --> 33:14.950
Even if you may die?

34:02.020 --> 34:03.190
Don't be scared, Chang.

34:12.180 --> 34:13.830
I'm getting you out now.

34:14.270 --> 34:15.110
Spare me.

34:15.750 --> 34:17.500
Spare me.

34:19.620 --> 34:20.470
Chang,

34:20.470 --> 34:22.430
you'll be free soon.

34:32.220 --> 34:33.390
Don't be scared, Chang.

34:38.100 --> 34:39.350
Take this decoction

34:41.540 --> 34:42.830
and you'll be all right.

35:06.950 --> 35:08.950
Don't be scared, Chang.

35:09.220 --> 35:11.020
Just don't be scared.

35:11.390 --> 35:15.750
Don't be scared, Chang.

35:55.220 --> 35:57.820
(Zhaomu Pavilion)

36:14.100 --> 36:14.940
Hey, young man.

36:17.790 --> 36:18.630
Maizi.

36:19.430 --> 36:20.990
Her Grace assigned me to serve you.

36:25.540 --> 36:26.380
Young man,

36:26.910 --> 36:28.790
you're the first one to live

36:28.950 --> 36:29.950
in the Sovereign's room

36:29.950 --> 36:30.990
over the centuries.

36:32.140 --> 36:33.100
You're so favored.

36:35.310 --> 36:36.150
If that's the case,

36:36.310 --> 36:37.270
I'm indeed favored.

36:39.950 --> 36:40.990
I've always wanted to ask.

36:41.620 --> 36:43.580
You were a spirit in the Mortal World.

36:44.390 --> 36:45.620
But why are you a mortal

36:45.950 --> 36:46.830
in the Spirit World?

36:47.430 --> 36:48.270
How did you do that?

36:49.390 --> 36:50.230
If you want to know,

36:50.870 --> 36:51.790
take me to Her Grace.

36:52.470 --> 36:54.950
She'll punish the guilty spirit today.

36:55.580 --> 36:56.430
That's too cruel

36:56.620 --> 36:57.460
to watch.

37:16.540 --> 37:18.460
(Execution Platform, the Void)

37:32.910 --> 37:33.750
Fang Chang.

37:50.500 --> 37:51.340
Fang Chang.

38:02.830 --> 38:03.870
I'm going

38:06.100 --> 38:07.700
to be annihilated, right?

38:17.100 --> 38:17.940
Very well.

38:19.470 --> 38:20.310
He Simu,

38:21.470 --> 38:22.310
bring it on!

38:24.060 --> 38:25.700
All you can do

38:26.750 --> 38:27.950
is annihilate those

38:27.950 --> 38:29.500
who you don't like.

38:30.750 --> 38:31.750
Do you think

38:32.390 --> 38:34.220
this will keep your throne forever?

38:34.300 --> 38:35.140
Do you think

38:35.140 --> 38:36.470
they'll really obey you?

38:37.950 --> 38:39.750
Everybody wants to replace you

38:40.390 --> 38:42.270
when you're weak.

38:44.140 --> 38:45.060
You only rely

38:45.540 --> 38:47.270
on your mighty power.

38:47.660 --> 38:49.060
A tyrant like you

38:49.060 --> 38:50.950
- deserves to die!
- Fang Chang.

38:52.180 --> 38:53.500
You violated our decrees

38:53.500 --> 38:54.340
to assassinate the Sovereign.

38:55.060 --> 38:56.500
Punishing you by law

38:56.870 --> 38:58.500
is the exact way to uphold justice.

38:58.870 --> 39:00.430
How dare you make wild remarks

39:00.430 --> 39:01.270
to slander Her Grace!

39:01.750 --> 39:02.590
It doesn't matter.

39:03.140 --> 39:04.020
Let him continue.

39:06.700 --> 39:08.180
I'm right here.

39:08.950 --> 39:10.830
If you're able to kill me,

39:11.700 --> 39:12.950
come and kill me.

39:20.140 --> 39:21.430
I thought

39:22.870 --> 39:24.620
you would have
more impressive last words.

39:26.020 --> 39:28.020
Fang Chang, Vice Lord
of Shanling Temple,

39:28.620 --> 39:30.100
colluded with a traitor

39:30.350 --> 39:31.350
to assassinate me.

39:31.350 --> 39:32.350
He violated Article 7

39:32.350 --> 39:33.830
of the Golden-wall Decrees, Treason.

39:34.390 --> 39:36.580
He'll be annihilated now.

39:39.310 --> 39:40.350
Any objections?

39:47.140 --> 39:48.310
He Simu,

39:49.580 --> 39:51.830
I'm not the only one
who wants to kill you.

39:52.700 --> 39:53.950
And him! Him!

39:53.950 --> 39:55.350
All of them!

39:59.830 --> 40:00.790
He Simu,

40:01.750 --> 40:02.790
remember this.

40:03.910 --> 40:05.020
The fate I have today

40:05.580 --> 40:07.180
will be yours tomorrow.

40:47.430 --> 40:48.390
A spirit has no senses.

40:49.180 --> 40:50.430
Why is he in such pain?

40:50.950 --> 40:52.990
That's the pain congealed
from spirit power.

40:53.470 --> 40:55.020
It's a punishment for guilty spirits.

41:40.920 --> 41:46.250
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

41:46.580 --> 41:50.830
♪Light encountered shadow♪

41:52.190 --> 41:57.560
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

41:57.860 --> 42:02.460
♪The unbreakable fate♪

42:03.550 --> 42:05.390
♪Suddenly cracked♪

42:17.600 --> 42:23.040
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

42:23.220 --> 42:27.550
♪Light encountered shadow♪

42:28.920 --> 42:34.310
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

42:34.540 --> 42:38.480
♪The unbreakable fate♪

42:40.250 --> 42:42.140
♪Suddenly cracked♪

42:44.800 --> 42:47.960
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

42:47.960 --> 42:50.490
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

42:50.490 --> 42:56.010
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

42:56.010 --> 42:59.250
♪Following fate's guidance♪

42:59.250 --> 43:04.110
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

43:04.450 --> 43:07.470
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

43:07.470 --> 43:10.290
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

43:10.550 --> 43:13.080
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

43:13.080 --> 43:18.500
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

43:18.670 --> 43:21.740
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

43:21.900 --> 43:26.800
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

43:27.010 --> 43:30.480
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
